  "title": "Sales & Project manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Salary + Commission + Allowances - $3500-$5500</li>\n  <li>6 working days, OT if needed</li>\n  <li>Will require to travel around Singapore</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop strategies to meet business goals and identify revenue opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Lead market analysis, business development, and material pricing for projects.</li>\n  <li>Manage project budgets, cost analysis, and ensure profitability.</li>\n  <li>Build strong relationships with suppliers, lead client presentations, and resolve disputes.</li>\n  <li>Mentor junior staff, collaborate with teams, and promote continuous improvement.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with laws and manage commercial risks effectively.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates with <strong>Commercial Management / Contract Negotiation / Interior Design / Construction</strong> or other related experiences are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
